Title: Bank for International Settlements Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for BIS statistical data (SDMX API).
    Central bank policy rates, effective exchange rates, property prices,
    debt securities, central bank assets. 29 dataflows covering global
    financial and economic statistics.
